This controller uses the `BlogPostService` to perform CRUD operations on the `BlogPost` class. The `createBlogPost` method creates a new blog post, the `getBlogPost` method retrieves a blog post by its ID, the `deleteBlogPost` method deletes a blog post by its ID, and the `updateBlogPost` method updates an existing blog post. The `MultipartHttpServletRequest` is used to handle file uploads. The controller also includes validation and error handling to ensure that the requests are properly formatted.
